  title Mi perfil
  body
    .container
      h1 Editar Perfil
      |  &#x9;
      hr
      |  &#x9;
      .row
        .col-md-3
          .text-center
            img.avatar.img-circle(src='https://d30y9cdsu7xlg0.cloudfront.net/png/404950-200.png', alt='avatar')

            h6 Cambiar foto

            input.form-control(type='file')

        .col-md-9.personal-info
          .alert.alert-info.alert-dismissable
            a.panel-close.close(data-dismiss='alert') &times;

            i.fa.fa-coffee
                       La contrase&ntilde;a es
            strong incorrecta
              porfavor vuelva a intentarlo

          h3 Informacion personal

          form.form-horizontal(role='form' method='post' href='/mi-usuario')
            .form-group
              label.col-lg-3.control-label Nombre:

              .col-lg-8
                input.form-control(type='text')

            .form-group
              label.col-lg-3.control-label Apellido:

              .col-lg-8
                input.form-control(type='text')

            .form-group
              label.col-lg-3.control-label Email:

              .col-lg-8
                input.form-control(type='text')

            .form-group
              .form-group
                label.col-md-3.control-label Nombre de usuario:

                .col-md-8
                  input.form-control(type='text')

              .form-group
                label.col-md-3.control-label Contrase&ntilde;a:

                .col-md-8
                  input.form-control(type='password')

              .form-group
                label.col-md-3.control-label Confirmar contrase&ntilde;a:

                .col-md-8
                  input.form-control(type='password')

              .form-group
                label.col-md-3.control-label

                .col-md-8
                  input.btn.btn-primary(value='Guardar Cambios', type='button')

                  span

                  input.btn.btn-default(value='Cancelar', type='reset')

